<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٥ - وَالشُّهَدَاء خَمْسَة.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٦ - من اغْتسل يَوْم الْجُمُعَة.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٧ -<span class="c5"> من قَالَ:</span> لَا إِلَه إِلَّا الله وَحده.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٨ -<span class="c5"> من قَالَ:</span> سُبْحَانَ الله فِي يَوْم <span class="c2">(٢٨ / ب)</span> مائَة مرّة حطت خطاياه.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٩ - السّفر قِطْعَة من الْعَذَاب.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>